comments: Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact to Morant's (MEM) body during his drive to the basket.
Poeltl (SAS) jumps from point A to point B into Morant's (MEM) body and the contact affects his driving shot attempt.
Adams (MEM) jumps vertically and absorbs the oncoming body contact from Murray (SAS) during his driving shot attempt. Adams avoids making contact to Murray's arm.
Adams (MEM) releases from his initial screening position and marginal contact occurs with White (SAS) as both players disengage from the pick.
Adams (MEM) and Poeltl (SAS) mutually engage in marginal contact during the rebound.
Poeltl (SAS) jumps A-B and makes contact with Morant's (MEM) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) firms up and makes marginal contact to Morant's (MEM) body during the screen off ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Murray (SAS) reaches in and makes contact with the ball during Morant's (MEM) dribble. The ball is last touched by Murray and possession is correctly awarded to MEM. There is no clear and conclusive evidence showing Morant touch the ball last before going out of bounds.
White (SAS) delivers contact to Morant's (MEM) body that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Poeltl (SAS) is slightly late to establish himself in a screening position in the path of Morant (MEM) but makes marginal contact to his body that doesnt affect his legal guarding position.
Jackson Jr. (MEM) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
